{"tid":1397134,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發] 聽日銅鑼灣一定好危險！","createTime":"2019-08-02T10:35:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T02:45:30.000Z","uid":39205,"like":1281,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":119,"replies":[{"pid":"07ce78034e4ee874805d119a1f31c1cfe5c3585a","tid":1397134,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:35:00.000Z","msg":"屌我政治中立架嘛，咁星期六梗係出銅仔呢啲高級地方架啦，諗住今個星期六約我女神去睇戲啦，點知佢無啦啦同我講聽日<span style=\"color: orange;\">維園有撐警集會</span>，我心諗關我撚事咩我又唔係個啲黃絲，好彩佢send埋張poster過黎睇。<br />\n<br />\n嘩屌我嚇撚到！原來係<span style=\"color: orange;\">有埋元朗個班白衫黑社會架</span>！之前聽啲黃絲朋友講話咩<span style=\"color: orange;\">警黑勾結</span>，我都唔撚信，你估拍戲咩？屌你雖然我唔係個啲黃絲姐，<span style=\"color: orange;\">個班白衫見人就打架喎</span>。<br />\n<br />\n屌見你班連登仔講野幾好笑有時上黎睇下，<span style=\"color: orange;\">點知咁大件事完全無人講</span>。都係我女神對我好，<span style=\"color: orange;\">我即刻send哂比我啲親戚朋友睇架啦</span>，叫佢地自己小心唔好出個邊啦唉。聽日都係約我女神去旺角算。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qKpwo6e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqKpwo6e.png&h=13984e03&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ef894c37ac6d3f3c2c065b3c14b229fa68e0e41c","tid":1397134,"uid":39205,"like":533,"dislike":1,"score":532,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:35:43.000Z","msg":"咁大個仔都未見過銅鑼灣一個人都無唔知有冇機會"},{"pid":"c6e4c87aa1d36f0e553ca46842291d124cb18553","tid":1397134,"uid":276175,"like":354,"dislike":2,"score":352,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:39:21.000Z","msg":"聽日千萬唔好去銅鑼灣！同佢地黑白分明！"},{"pid":"01578c28aae191a43121ee236c769153179242b7","tid":1397134,"uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:42:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fad4bd2619a30f80738b074ff3998d53407473fe","tid":1397134,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:42:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"bfc45a0860a25bca092a965c68509605267b2d4e","tid":1397134,"uid":69810,"like":60,"dislike":1,"score":59,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-02T10:42: